{"tid":436522,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"絕地求生PubG討論區（1）","createTime":"2017-10-15T08:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T05:31:33.000Z","uid":62495,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1b347f99e4edd66a1785ca8535a6bd5d4cb94980","tid":436522,"uid":62495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T08:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/15/161358_42e5d0c529a0956e153658631cbb02eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F15%2F161358_42e5d0c529a0956e153658631cbb02eb.jpg&h=57915de8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每一局遊戲大約有100名玩家參與，且在這個大型死亡競賽中爭取活至最後，可以選擇第一人稱、第三人稱，和每隊人數不同的遊戲模式。而無論在哪種情況下，生存至最後的一人或團隊都會贏得比賽。在每局比賽開始時，玩家所控制的角色都會在沒有攜帶任何物品的情況下跳傘至島上。着陸後，玩家便能搜尋建築物和其他場所，從而獲取隨機分佈在整個地圖上的武器、車輛及其他裝備。其後，玩家需要選擇繼續保持隱藏以免被其他玩家殺死或追捕，並繼續尋找更多裝備，或者追捕及殺害其他玩家且搶走他們的裝備。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> WINNER WINNER ,CHICKEN DINNER!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一隻考驗人性醜惡，道德淪亡的生存遊戲。不論單人或隊伍形式，你所面對的不單是敵人，亦會是隊友。不幸的，自己亦會困亦絕地中。<br />\n<br />\n大家有什麼趣事或所見所聞，不妨互相分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f82b11e4bfa3418f9e4fa9fa9d7bd70ded2a5cb","tid":436522,"uid":62495,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T08:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/15/162053_d82b7c030a443b5ef4a54a8d76bb2a07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F15%2F162053_d82b7c030a443b5ef4a54a8d76bb2a07.jpg&h=28661a44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先分享一下吃雞的心情<br />\n打完 手都震埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n收到最後一圈，邊個俾人發現位置就死先。 <br />\n好在圈收我附近，敵人無辦法要跑。<br />\n<br />\n我得2Lv頭2Lv甲，今次吃雞靠幸運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c46109e1ea8d8f3e4f47d54cd5c3b277de834a","tid":436522,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T12:45:15.000Z","msg":"title 用ping 仲好"},{"pid":"10b555d763b67c0f712ad082ae1a706285320376","tid":436522,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T12:47:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>title 用pubg 仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote>"},{"pid":"9115ffc5339e376456862b306d3a366b4cc6a720","tid":436522,"uid":29781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:40:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6i1y13GjN1M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6i1y13GjN1M&d=8igjPI8HX2AHJJWV7xU7oozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=70590ce5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6i1y13GjN1M</a><br />\n大陸真係唔知醜"},{"pid":"57bb845645038404e0c8ad322aa4b250dccc44cb","tid":436522,"uid":42729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T05:31:33.000Z","msg":"有冇人有斷線問題<br />\n成日玩玩下 中途就斷線<br />\n雖然可以連得返 但場場都斷 斷得好密<br />\n求解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}